(140, '<000001d0af29$7839fad0$68adf070$@buaa.edu.cn>', '上机成绩请与附件合并', '<html xmlns:v="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml" xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" xmlns:m="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40"><head><meta http-equiv=Content-Type content="text/html; charset=gb2312"><meta name=Generator content="Microsoft Word 14 (filtered medium)"><style><!--\r\n/* Font Definitions */\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:宋体;\r\n	panose-1:2 1 6 0 3 1 1 1 1 1;}\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:宋体;\r\n	panose-1:2 1 6 0 3 1 1 1 1 1;}\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:Calibri;\r\n	panose-1:2 15 5 2 2 2 4 3 2 4;}\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:"\\@宋体";\r\n	panose-1:2 1 6 0 3 1 1 1 1 1;}\r\n/* Style Definitions */\r\np.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\r\n	{margin:0cm;\r\n	margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	text-align:justify;\r\n	text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\n	font-size:10.5pt;\r\n	font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";}\r\na:link, span.MsoHyperlink\r\n	{mso-style-priority:99;\r\n	color:blue;\r\n	text-decoration:underline;}\r\na:visited, span.MsoHyperlinkFollowed\r\n	{mso-style-priority:99;\r\n	color:purple;\r\n	text-decoration:underline;}\r\nspan.EmailStyle17\r\n	{mso-style-type:personal;\r\n	font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";\r\n	color:windowtext;}\r\nspan.EmailStyle18\r\n	{mso-style-type:personal-reply;\r\n	font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";\r\n	color:#1F497D;}\r\n.MsoChpDefault\r\n	{mso-style-type:export-only;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;}\r\n@page WordSection1\r\n	{size:612.0pt 792.0pt;\r\n	margin:72.0pt 90.0pt 72.0pt 90.0pt;}\r\ndiv.WordSection1\r\n	{page:WordSection1;}\r\n--></style><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<o:shapedefaults v:ext="edit" spidmax="1026" />\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<o:shapelayout v:ext="edit">\r\n<o:idmap v:ext="edit" data="1" />\r\n</o:shapelayout></xml><![endif]--></head><body lang=ZH-CN link=blue vlink=purple style=''text-justify-trim:punctuation''><div class=WordSection1><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-family:宋体;color:#1F497D''>附件是我掌握的四次考勤情况。其中每请假一次扣</span><span lang=EN-US style=''color:#1F497D''>1</span><span style=''font-family:宋体;color:#1F497D''>分。</span><span lang=EN-US style=''color:#1F497D''><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-family:宋体;color:#1F497D''>我记得最后一次有一批同学集体请假，但假条好像报给了黎健成。请黎健成对相关同学的成绩作相应的修改。</span><span lang=EN-US style=''color:#1F497D''><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style=''color:#1F497D''>8</span><span style=''font-family:宋体;color:#1F497D''>次上机的成绩也请合并到这个</span><span lang=EN-US style=''color:#1F497D''>EXCEL</span><span style=''font-family:宋体;color:#1F497D''>表格中来，以便后期统计成绩。</span><span lang=EN-US style=''color:#1F497D''><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-family:宋体;color:#1F497D''>谢谢！</span><span lang=EN-US style=''color:#1F497D''><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style=''color:#1F497D''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-family:宋体;color:#1F497D''>邵兵</span><span lang=EN-US style=''color:#1F497D''><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style=''color:#1F497D''><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><div><div style=''border:none;border-top:solid #B5C4DF 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0cm 0cm 0cm''><p class=MsoNormal align=left style=''text-align:left''><b><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体''>发件人<span lang=EN-US>:</span></span></b><span lang=EN-US style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体''> shaobing [mailto:shaobing@buaa.edu.cn] <br></span><b><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体''>发送时间<span lang=EN-US>:</span></span></b><span lang=EN-US style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体''> 2015</span><span style=''font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体''>年<span lang=EN-US>6</span>月<span lang=EN-US>25</span>日<span lang=EN-US> 17:09<br></span><b>收件人<span lang=EN-US>:</span></b><span lang=EN-US> 609691039@qq.com; lijiancheng@buaa.edu.cn<br></span><b>主题<span lang=EN-US>:</span></b><span lang=EN-US> </span>关于<span lang=EN-US>C#</span>课程的收尾工作<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></div></div><p class=MsoNormal align=left style=''text-align:left''><span lang=EN-US><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-family:宋体''>黎健成、王鹏程：</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=''font-family:宋体''>二位好！</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=''font-family:宋体''>在大家的努力下，我们的《</span><span lang=EN-US>C#</span><span style=''font-family:宋体''>程序设计》课程已于今天顺利考试结束。</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=''font-family:宋体''>黎健成由于毕业缘故，不一定能有时间来改卷子，所以剩下的工作恐怕得拜托王鹏程了。</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=''font-family:宋体''>我一直都有时间的。请问王鹏程什么时候方便？如果可能的话，改卷子的时候最好多找几个同学来帮忙，一个人负责几道题，流水作业会很快的。</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=''font-family:宋体''>另外，还请你们二位把之前实验课上机的成绩统计出来发给我。考勤的统计我已经有了。</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=''font-family:宋体''>按照惯例，你们二位的</span><span lang=EN-US>TA</span><span style=''font-family:宋体''>费用应该在下个学期才能发放。王鹏程的问题不大，黎健成的由于届时没有学籍了，所以最好能找个在学的朋友，我们把费用发到他的账户，他再提现转给你，因为学院只能走帐不能直接提现的。</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=''font-family:宋体''>最后，对一个学期以来二位的辛勤工作表示由衷的感谢！</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-family:宋体''>邵兵</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>', '"shaobing"|shaobing@buaa.edu.cn\r;', '609691039@qq.com', 0, NULL, 0, '2015-06-29 14:00:45'),
