(241, '<1612961492.358805.1434408223418.JavaMail.oschina@liubc>', '开源中国一周精彩回顾 ?? 6月26', '<h2 style="color: #008000; margin: 10px 0;">开源中国 ( <a href="http://www.oschina.net/?from=20150614">www.oschina.net</a> ) 一周精彩回顾</h2>\r\n<h2 style="color: #008000; margin: 10px 0;"></h2>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">本周活动推荐：</span></p>\r\n<p class="p2"><span class="s2">【线上】6月16日&nbsp;cSphere 希云 Docker 实训课程第二讲最后报名&nbsp;<a href="http://www.oschina.net/news/63215/csphere-docker-second"><span class="s3">http://www.oschina.net/news/63215/csphere-docker-second</span></a>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">【广州】6月26日-27日 第十届&ldquo;开源中国 开源世界&rdquo;高峰论坛议程</span><span class="s4"> <a href="http://www.oschina.net/ocow2015"><span class="s5">http://www.oschina.net/ocow2015</span></a></span><span class="s1">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="p2"><span class="s2">【北京】Velocity China 2015 技术大会 &ndash; 门票赠送/购票优惠&nbsp;<a href="http://www.oschina.net/news/63197/velocity-china-2015"><span class="s3">http://www.oschina.net/news/63197/velocity-china-2015</span></a></span><span class="s6">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="p2"><span class="s2">【北京】2015 HTML5游戏开发者大赛 -门票限时免费发放&nbsp;<a href="http://city.oschina.net/beijing/event/239262"><span class="s3">http://city.oschina.net/beijing/event/239262</span></a>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p2"><span class="s2">【北京】MobileTesting Summit China 中国移动测试技术大会&nbsp;<a href="http://city.oschina.net/beijing/event/238272"><span class="s3">http://city.oschina.net/beijing/event/238272</span></a>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<ul style="list-style-type: none; padding: 0; margin: 10px 0 0 0;">\r\n<li style="margin: 20px 0;"> <span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: #008000; font-weight: bold; font-family: Courier New;">2015-06-14</span> <span style="font-weight: bold; margin: 2px 10px 5px 0; display: block;"><a href="http://www.oschina.net/p/inception?from=20150614">Inception &mdash;&mdash; Android 设备的自动配置工具</a></span> <span style="color: #666; font