(324, '<001201d09c32$bafa2d40$30ee87c0$@buaa.edu.cn>', '关于C#课程的课堂考勤情况公布', '<html xmlns:v="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml" xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" xmlns:x="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel" xmlns:m="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40"><head><meta http-equiv=Content-Type content="text/html; charset=gb2312"><meta name=Generator content="Microsoft Word 14 (filtered medium)"><style><!--\r\n/* Font Definitions */\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:宋体;\r\n	panose-1:2 1 6 0 3 1 1 1 1 1;}\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:宋体;\r\n	panose-1:2 1 6 0 3 1 1 1 1 1;}\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:Calibri;\r\n	panose-1:2 15 5 2 2 2 4 3 2 4;}\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-family:"\\@宋体";\r\n	panose-1:2 1 6 0 3 1 1 1 1 1;}\r\n/* Style Definitions */\r\np.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\r\n	{margin:0cm;\r\n	margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	text-align:justify;\r\n	text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\n	font-size:10.5pt;\r\n	font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";}\r\na:link, span.MsoHyperlink\r\n	{mso-style-priority:99;\r\n	color:blue;\r\n	text-decoration:underline;}\r\na:visited, span.MsoHyperlinkFollowed\r\n	{mso-style-priority:99;\r\n	color:purple;\r\n	text-decoration:underline;}\r\nspan.EmailStyle17\r\n	{mso-style-type:personal-compose;\r\n	font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";\r\n	color:windowtext;}\r\n.MsoChpDefault\r\n	{mso-style-type:export-only;\r\n	font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";}\r\n/* Page Definitions */\r\n@page WordSection1\r\n	{size:612.0pt 792.0pt;\r\n	margin:72.0pt 90.0pt 72.0pt 90.0pt;}\r\ndiv.WordSection1\r\n	{page:WordSection1;}\r\n--></style><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<o:shapedefaults v:ext="edit" spidmax="1026" />\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<o:shapelayout v:ext="edit">\r\n<o:idmap v:ext="edit" data="1" />\r\n</o:shapelayout></xml><![endif]--></head><body lang=ZH-CN link=blue vlink=purple style=''text-justify-trim:punctuation''><div class=WordSection1><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-family:宋体''>各位同学：</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal style=''text-indent:21.6pt''><span style=''font-family:宋体''>从</span><span lang=EN-US>4</span><span style=''font-family:宋体''>月底到现在，我在课堂上采用上交纸条签到、课堂作业等方式进行了三次考勤，结果发现每次的出勤率大概都在百分之七十多一点儿。除去往届重修、外系选修者之外，有</span><span lang=EN-US>15</span><span style=''font-family:宋体''>名同学甚至一次都没到过。</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal style=''text-indent:21.6pt''><span style=''font-family:宋体''>课堂教学是大学教育中非常重要的环节。北航教务处在《学生手册》中也明确要求“凡缺勤超过课程教学学时数的三分之一者，不得参加本课程的期末考核，须重修。”如果一个学生连课都不上，很难想象能学到扎实的理论基础（当然不排除个别奇才的存在）。根据以往软件学院的同学情况看，每年都会有学生被淘汰的，而被淘汰者往往都是上课缺席者。因此，希望大家能够引起足够的重视！</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal style=''text-indent:21.6pt''><span style=''font-family:宋体''>从下次课开始，我将不再采用课堂全员检查的办法，而准备采用抽检的方式考勤，而抽检的重点将是下面名单中公布的同学（重修者除外）。凡是缺席次数超过</span><span lang=EN-US>5</span><span style=''font-family:宋体''>次者，将不得参加本课程期末考试！</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal style=''text-indent:21.6pt''><span style=''font-family:宋体''>敬请周知！</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal style=''text-indent:21.6pt''><span lang=EN-US><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style=''font-family:宋体''>邵兵</span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><table class=MsoNormalTable border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=793 style=''width:475.65pt;margin-left:-1.05pt;border-collapse:collapse''><tr style=''height:27.6pt''><td width=55 nowrap style=''width:33.0pt;border:solid black 1.0pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:27.6pt''><p class=MsoNormal align=center style=''text-align:center''><span style=''font-family:宋体;color:black''>序号<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></td><td width=100 nowrap style=''width:59.9pt;border:solid black 1.0pt;border-left:none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:27.6pt''><p class=Mso